{"tid":2201601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"慢必代快必擺街站 轟以言入罪","createTime":"2020-09-14T02:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T03:02:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b847675ab77613ed4d028a4ba369bd41c197adf1","tid":2201601,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/HX3B7RW2NRCFVEPV4N2L6PQQOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FHX3B7RW2NRCFVEPV4N2L6PQQOQ%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8EzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=9e86f6d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FHX3B7RW2NRCFVEPV4N2L6PQQOQ%2F&h=270bf491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/HX3B7RW2NRCFVEPV4N2L6PQQOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n慢必代快必擺街站 轟以言入罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志被控五項發表煽動文字罪及一項公眾地方擾亂秩序罪，。。。。。。。。。。。，有市民戴上「快必」譚得志面具，象徵「人人都是譚得志」，不滿政府將譚以言入罪。<br />\n<br />\n人民力量昨午4時在觀塘裕民坊和藍田啟田商場外擺設街站，向街坊派口罩和傳單。兩區均有數架警車在旁戒備，在場有市民戴上「快必」譚得志面具，象徵「人人都是譚得志」，眾人高叫「釋放快必」、「撐快必，撐到底」、「想我收聲，我更大聲」等口號，亦有人叫「光復香港，時代革命」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vzHpUsOwuHQ_k203hVknHVeAKiw=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5F7GCJBK5GTJO5JX2WFNTIFJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvzHpUsOwuHQ_k203hVknHVeAKiw%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5F7GCJBK5GTJO5JX2WFNTIFJU.jpg&h=e543e47e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「慢必」陳志全昨擺街站向街坊派口罩和傳單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民叫口號撐快必<br />\n<br />\n陳志全指擺抗疫街站少不免批評政府抗疫失敗，「如果政府做得好，我返屋企瞓覺啦」，斥特首林鄭月娥將檢測提升至反政府層次，現又改口稱「全民檢測」為「普及檢測」，因現時參與人數不足全港人口四分一，「點解唔使錢都係咁少人去？因為連藍絲都信唔過你」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。「冇得驚冇得計」，又指高等法院周四將審理譚的保釋上訴，形容今次許勝不許敗，敗訴最少要坐到11月，成功則可立即保釋。"},{"pid":"52650cacc439f177af40d7e0405f6c9939b5a5c9","tid":2201601,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467c83af6581070122330a7872e367273bf968ce","tid":2201601,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"一級奸爸爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b96d6138c02fdccc21297e2f1bc710ffe478aef","tid":2201601,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467c83af6581070122330a7872e367273bf968ce","tid":2201601,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"一級奸爸爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"不枉細個集集支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbb6d351dbf113f583e415ac3b0a1aef3b098fd","tid":2201601,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467c83af6581070122330a7872e367273bf968ce","tid":2201601,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"一級奸爸爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1246e92f38c06f0a7b05476cc6dec4f865615b9e","tid":2201601,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6b26efe49b78e1d8147ce8ea1b55641e459ebe0","tid":2201601,"uid":331739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"人力先係真抗爭派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92368a72381ba96e4dc30f28264b74138925996e","tid":2201601,"uid":292799,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6b26efe4